and it seems like ya can&#39;t go two weeks without someone that thinks 
they know more, or their &quot;theories&quot; are more valid, or someone that 
believes for whatever reason they are the box/EVP/paranormal expert. 
I&#39;ve had enough, these groups are pointless, and I&#39;m tired of the 
BS. There is always these incessant arguements with those that seem 
to think they know better than anyone else. Maybe it&#39;s just me, and 
my over reactions, but at this point, I don&#39;t care, enough is 
enough. So ya want the group? I don&#39;t actually own it due to one of 
these idiotic arguements, but have at it, cuz I ain&#39;t playing this 
game anymore. I&#39;ll continue my own work, in my own time, and in my 
own way.
&gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt; Frank-S
